ing: salt and ground black pepper to taste
des: "Spicy arugula is a delightful parsley alternative in this hummus. Excellent as a vegetable dip or a sandwich spread."
ins: Place garbanzo beans, arugula, tahini, lemon juice, and garlic in a food processor; pulse until garbanzo beans are chopped. Slowly drizzle olive oil into garbanzo bean mixture while blending until mixture is smooth. Season with salt and pepper.
